overview.longBusinessSummary: Invitation Homes, an S&P 500 company, is the nation's premier single-family home leasing and management company, meeting changing lifestyle demands by providing access to high-quality homes with valued features such as close proximity to jobs and access to good schools. Our purpose, Unlock the power of home, reflects our commitment to providing living solutions and Genuine CARE to the growing share of people who count on the flexibility and savings of leasing a home.
